NAME
    Module::Install::AutoProvidesFromCompilation

SYNOPSIS
        use inc::Module::Install;
        name 'Example';
        all_from 'lib/Example.pm'
        auto_provides_from_compilation();
        WriteAll;

DESCRIPTION
    Ensures that your META.yml contains provides information for every class
    in your lib/ directory.

